=== 0.7.0 (2012-07-10)

* Added the ability to save and load PdfMasher projects. (#15)
* Tweaked Fairware reminders.
* Improved Debian packaging. [Linux]
* Upgraded minimum requirements to Ubuntu 12.04.

=== 0.6.3 (2011-10-07)

* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.6.2 (2011-09-05)

* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.
* Fixed bug making TOC and footnotes in MOBI link to wrong locations.

=== 0.6.1 (2011-08-30)

* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.
* Fixed a crash on clicking the page view.
* Fixed a crash on ebook generation.
* Fixed a bug causing the first character(s) of each line to be removed when reading a PDF.

=== 0.6.0 (2011-08-22)

* Added automatic page breaks for title elements (level 1 and 2).
* Added automatic TOC generation for title elements(level 1 and 2). (#4)
* Improved text layout detection in PDFs.
* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.5.0 (2011-08-18)

* Added the ability to generate MOBI and EPUB documents (using code from Calibre).
* Changed the license from BSD to GPL (Calibre is GPL).
* Fixed a memory usage problem.

=== 0.4.0 (2011-08-09)

* Added a new Page View feature, which is really cool.
* Moved the Edit/Build tab view to the right to leave more space to the page view.
* Title elements now have multiple levels (1 to 6)
* Added keyboard bindings to quickly set element states.
* Improved text layout detection in PDFs.
* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.3.0 (2011-07-26)

* Added a new flag: "To Fix".
* Added keyboard shortcuts for quickly flagging elements.
* Improved text layout detection in PDFs.
* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.2.1 (2011-07-15)

* Fixed a bug where title elements wouldn't correctly be wrapped. (#3)
* Fixed a bug where generating markdown for elements with footnotes more than once would make a mess.
* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.2.0 (2011-07-10)

* Made the PDF opening progress smooth (progress bar).
* Added a Markdown intermediate step in the build process.
* Added a Text Length column.
* Made the error message when opening a non-PDF file more friendly.
* Fixed a bug making the order of some text parts to be mixed up.
* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.

=== 0.1.2 (2011-07-07)

* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.
* Fixed a bug where there would sometimes be no space character between words.
* Added auto-update support with Sparkle. [Mac OS X]

=== 0.1.1 (2011-06-27)

* Fixed bugs preventing some PDFs to be read.
* Correctly set the encoding of resulting HTML files.

=== 0.1.0 (2011-06-21)

* Initial preview release.
